description:
El Quest Macquarie Park ofrece conexión WiFi gratuita y se encuentra a solo 500 metros de la estación de tren de Macquarie Park, que conecta con el centro de Sídney. El establecimiento alberga un centro de fitness.

El Quest Macquarie Park se halla a 20 minutos a pie del centro comercial Macquarie Centre, que alberga una gran variedad de tiendas, cafeterías, restaurantes, una pista de patinaje sobre hielo y un cine. La Universidad Macquarie se encuentra a 5 minutos en coche y el aeropuerto de Sídney, a 30 minutos en coche.

El establecimiento ofrece estudios independientes y apartamentos de 1 y 2 dormitorios. Todas disponen de aire acondicionado, salón, escritorio, mesa de comedor y TV de pantalla plana vía satélite con reproductor de DVD. El apartamento estudio tiene una zona de cocina con fogones y lavavajillas. Los apartamentos de 1 y 2 dormitorios disponen de lavadora y cocina totalmente equipada con horno.

El establecimiento también cuenta con zona de barbacoa. Se ofrece servicio de entrega de comestibles.

description:
Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park combines modern comforts with calming ambience, perfect for the savvy business traveller. Superbly located just a 20-minute drive to Sydney CBD and only a few minutes from major business parks, Macquarie University and Macquarie Shopping University, we're in the heart of a bustling area.

Situated in the heart of Macquarie Business Park and adjacent to Macquarie University Hospital, Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is the perfect home base for business travellers. Within an easy reach to Sydney CBD by car or train.

Relax after a busy day's work or sightseeing in your spacious, modern room at Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park.


Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is undergoing an exciting refresh to enhance our accommodation rooms and public spaces.
We will continue to provide exceptional service, whilst keeping disturbance to a minimum. Intermittent noise may be experienced between the hours of 10am to 5pm, Monday to Friday.

We look forward to sharing our amazing new product with you, with the completion of the project in mid-November.

The Ibis Kitchen & Bar serves a buffet breakfast and an a la carte lunch and dinner. Meal and Beverage options are available 24 hours a day with a late-night menu available.

Boasting free WiFi, Hotel Urban St Leonards is a boutique-style hotel offering luxuriously comfortable rooms on Sydney’s North Shore. Facilities include a café and bar, and fitness centre.

Each room includes a flat-screen TV, premium bathroom products and luxury linen. Sweet Urban rooms also feature a private spa bath, a large balcony and scenic water views.

Urban St Leonards Hotel is less than 5 minutes’ walk from Royal North Shore Hospital and North Shore Private Hospital. Mater Hospital is less than 5 minutes’ drive away.

El Holiday Inn Express está situado en el centro de negocios de Macquarie Park, a 9 minutos a pie del centro comercial Macquarie Centre, que alberga una gran variedad de sitios para comer y tiendas de moda. El centro de la ciudad de Sídney está a 20 minutos en coche o a 35 minutos en tren.

Todas las habitaciones están equipadas con un espacio de trabajo práctico y moderno que incluye escritorio, silla ergonómica y 4 puertos USB. También disponen de TV LCD de 40 pulgadas, set de té y café, caja fuerte y utensilios de planchado. En todas las habitaciones hay baño privado con ducha amplia a ras de suelo y secador de pelo de alta calidad.

description:
El Quest Macquarie Park ofrece conexión WiFi gratuita y se encuentra a solo 500 metros de la estación de tren de Macquarie Park, que conecta con el centro de Sídney. El establecimiento alberga un centro de fitness.

El Quest Macquarie Park se halla a 20 minutos a pie del centro comercial Macquarie Centre, que alberga una gran variedad de tiendas, cafeterías, restaurantes, una pista de patinaje sobre hielo y un cine. La Universidad Macquarie se encuentra a 5 minutos en coche y el aeropuerto de Sídney, a 30 minutos en coche.

El establecimiento ofrece estudios independientes y apartamentos de 1 y 2 dormitorios. Todas disponen de aire acondicionado, salón, escritorio, mesa de comedor y TV de pantalla plana vía satélite con reproductor de DVD. El apartamento estudio tiene una zona de cocina con fogones y lavavajillas. Los apartamentos de 1 y 2 dormitorios disponen de lavadora y cocina totalmente equipada con horno.

El establecimiento también cuenta con zona de barbacoa. Se ofrece servicio de entrega de comestibles.

description:
Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park combines modern comforts with calming ambience, perfect for the savvy business traveller. Superbly located just a 20-minute drive to Sydney CBD and only a few minutes from major business parks, Macquarie University and Macquarie Shopping University, we're in the heart of a bustling area.

Situated in the heart of Macquarie Business Park and adjacent to Macquarie University Hospital, Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is the perfect home base for business travellers. Within an easy reach to Sydney CBD by car or train.

Relax after a busy day's work or sightseeing in your spacious, modern room at Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park.


Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is undergoing an exciting refresh to enhance our accommodation rooms and public spaces.
We will continue to provide exceptional service, whilst keeping disturbance to a minimum. Intermittent noise may be experienced between the hours of 10am to 5pm, Monday to Friday.

We look forward to sharing our amazing new product with you, with the completion of the project in mid-November.

El restaurante de Lachlan ofrece menú a la carta para el desayuno, el almuerzo y la cena. El bar salón es el lugar perfecto para tomar una copa por la noche.

description:
Offering air-conditioned rooms with a flat-screen TV and an iPod dock, Hotel Ibis Thornleigh is just 750 metres from Thornleigh Railway Station. It features a 24-hour front desk, a restaurant and a bar. Sydney Adventist Hospital is a 4-minute drive away.

A refrigerator, tea and coffee maker and work desk is standard in all rooms. Each room has a bathroom with a hairdryer and guest toiletries.

Ibis Hotel Thornleigh is 30 minutes’ drive from central Sydney, and 40 minutes’ drive from Sydney Airport. Lane Cove National Park is a 15-minute drive away.

The Ibis Kitchen & Bar serves a buffet breakfast and an a la carte lunch and dinner. Meal and Beverage options are available 24 hours a day with a late-night menu available.

Featuring an outdoor pool and ample free parking space, Royal Pacific Hotel is just 4 minutes’ drive from Chatswood's Westfield Shopping Centre. It features self-contained rooms offering a flat-screen TV.

Royal Pacific Hotel is only 5 minutes’ walk from Artarmon Train Station and 15 minutes’ drive from Sydney’s city centre, Sydney Harbour Bridge and Luna Park. Sydney Airport is a 30-minute drive away.

The air-conditioned rooms include tea/coffee making facilities and a refrigerator. Each has a seating area, a work desk and a bathroom with a hairdryer and guest toiletries.

Guests can work out in the fitness centre or enjoy an outdoor meal in the BBQ area.

Boasting free WiFi, Hotel Urban St Leonards is a boutique-style hotel offering luxuriously comfortable rooms on Sydney’s North Shore. Facilities include a café and bar, and fitness centre.

description:
Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park combines modern comforts with calming ambience, perfect for the savvy business traveller. Superbly located just a 20-minute drive to Sydney CBD and only a few minutes from major business parks, Macquarie University and Macquarie Shopping University, we're in the heart of a bustling area.

La Universidad Macquarie se encuentra a 5 minutos en coche y el aeropuerto de Sídney, a 30 minutos en coche.

description:
Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park combines modern comforts with calming ambience, perfect for the savvy business traveller. Superbly located just a 20-minute drive to Sydney CBD and only a few minutes from major business parks, Macquarie University and Macquarie Shopping University, we're in the heart of a bustling area.

Situated in the heart of Macquarie Business Park and adjacent to Macquarie University Hospital, Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is the perfect home base for business travellers. Within an easy reach to Sydney CBD by car or train.

Relax after a busy day's work or sightseeing in your spacious, modern room at Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park.


Mercure Sydney Macquarie Park is undergoing an exciting refresh to enhance our accommodation rooms and public spaces.

Holiday Inn Parramatta is within walking distance from Westfield Parramatta Shopping Centre, BankWest Stadium, Eat Street and the Parramatta Railway Station. It is a 30-minute drive from the Sydney city centre and Sydney Airport.

Rooms at the Holiday Inn Parramatta are spacious and all feature air conditioning, a flat-screen TV and a desk. The One-Bedroom Suites offer a spa bath plus a separate lounge area with a sofa bed and a coffee machine.

Guests have access to an outdoor heated swimming pool and jacuzzi, plus complimentary WiFi throughout the entire hotel. Secure car parking is offered on site for additional charge of AU $20 per night.

The on-site restaurant Twenty One Fifty is open on weekdays for a la carte lunch and dinner, and 7 days a week for both a la carte and full buffet breakfast.

PARKROYAL Parramatta is located in the popular Church Street dining and shopping precinct in Parramatta, Western Sydney. It features free WiFi throughout and a fitness centre.

All air-conditioned rooms at the PARKROYAL Parramatta offer city views. Each features cable TV, tea and coffee making facilities and a flat screen TV.

Other amenities include a business centre, concierge service and laundry facilities and a swimming pool.

TABLE:30 Restaurant offers views of the lobby atrium, and serves an extensive menu for breakfast and dinner. BAR: 30 is the perfect place to relax with a cocktail.

Riverside Theatre is a 5-minute walk away and Parramatta Train Station is a 10-minute walk. Rosehill Gardens Racecourse is a 5-minute drive away. Sydney Olympic Park, Raging Waters Sydney and the ANZ Stadium are a 15-minute drive.

El Quest Macquarie Park ofrece conexión WiFi gratuita y se encuentra a solo 500 metros de la estación de tren de Macquarie Park, que conecta con el centro de Sídney. El establecimiento alberga un centro de fitness.

El Quest Macquarie Park se halla a 20 minutos a pie del centro comercial Macquarie Centre, que alberga una gran variedad de tiendas, cafeterías, restaurantes, una pista de patinaje sobre hielo y un cine. El apartamento estudio tiene una zona de cocina con fogones y lavavajillas. Los apartamentos de 1 y 2 dormitorios disponen de lavadora y cocina totalmente equipada con horno.

El establecimiento también cuenta con zona de barbacoa. Se ofrece servicio de entrega de comestibles.

description:
Rosehill Hotel se encuentra en Sídney, a 3,9 km de Western Sydney Stadium, y ofrece alojamiento con jardín, parking privado gratis, bar y casino. El hotel tiene wifi gratis y está a unos 6,2 km de Estadio ANZ y a 6,5 km de Qudos Bank Arena. El alojamiento dispone de ocio nocturno y cajero automático.

En el hotel, todas las habitaciones están equipadas con armario, TV de pantalla plana, baño compartido, ropa de cama y toallas.

Rosehill Hotel ofrece barbacoa.

Estadio Sydney Showground está a 6,8 km del alojamiento, y Bicentennial Park está a 8 km. El aeropuerto más cercano (Aeropuerto Kingsford Smith de Sídney) está a 23 km del alojamiento.

description:
El Greenwich Inn se encuentra a 10 minutos en coche del distrito financiero central de Sídney y ofrece habitaciones con aire acondicionado, TV por cable y conexión Wi-Fi. Ofrece aparcamiento cubierto.

El Motel Greenwich Inn está situado en el centro de la costa baja norte de Sídney, a 10 minutos a pie de la estación de tren de St. Leonards. El aeropuerto internacional de Sídney está a 25 minutos en coche.

Las habitaciones están bien equipadas y cuentan con zona de trabajo, nevera y set de té y café. El baño privado incluye secador de pelo y ducha.

Los huéspedes pueden acceder a internet en la cafetería, que ofrece aperitivos ligeros todos los días. También hay una lavandería automática de autoservicio y utensilios de planchado. La cafetería solo sirve desayunos. Recién reformado.
